data.description:
This home is conveniently located in the Viewmont area of Hickory - waterfront neighborhood gives you the freedom to enjoy Lake Hickory from your back door. Very desirable area! 
Main level has open concept living - Large family room, kitchen & breakfast nook, formal dining and flex room (office or den) and a wet bar. Kitchen opens onto a large covered deck that gives you plenty of entertaining space - very private setting with a large backyard.
Upstairs are four bedrooms and two bathrooms - very nice layout with privacy for each room.
Primary bedroom has tray ceilings with extra large bathroom, jetted tub, beautiful bay window, and walk-in closet.
The fourth bedroom can be a flex room - the closet currently holds washer/dryer.
